title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Lay a Proper Foundation in New Listings
content:
There's a new entrant in the Los Santos high-end real estate scene, and they're making moves into some of the most exclusive neighborhoods.

Clear out squatters, procure construction materials, and motivate contractors in New Listings — three new missions now available in GTA Online that bestow double GTA$ and RP.

Help Prix Luxury Real Estate by completing all three, and you’ll be granted their preferred rate — a GTA$2,000,000 discount — when these properties hit the market in December.
